JOHANNESBURG - Lobby group AfriForum on Friday rejected AgriSA's report suggesting farm murders are at their lowest levels in 19 years. AfriForum says its own statistics show there is in fact an increase in farm murders and attacks over the past four years. Organisations like AfriForum claim that many white South Africans are victims of farm murders. But AgriSA insists the murders are not just concentrated to one racial group. Watch the full video above. eNCA